\left[\forall_{l \in \{\varepsilon + 1~\ldotp \ldotp~2^{t - 1}\}}~\left(\frac{1}{\left(l - \left(2^{t} \cdot \delta\right)\right)^{2}} \in \mathbb{C}\right)\right] \Rightarrow \left(\left(\sum_{l=\varepsilon + 1}^{2^{t - 1}} \frac{1}{\left(l - \left(2^{t} \cdot \delta\right)\right)^{2}}\right) \in \mathbb{C}\right)